\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Prologue: Solraheen ends himself by calling in a comet of the night to bury him in the mountains.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 He sits in the mountains watching a great battle on the black plain.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The demons sustain themselves with feasting.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 The holies sustain themselves by drawing the rivers and the lands dry.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Solraheen cries.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s time to end it.}
