\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The demons play for tricks! They draw themselves out of position to play for tricks! They can\u8217\'92t respect an opponent. That\u8217\'92s why we\u8217\'92ll win!\u8221\'94 Confidence, but Solraheen could see his spark. It was despairing.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Demonhost wont assassinate him and break the Oldest Truce as he treats with demon generals.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Meets with Elrahet and Lora on the mountain.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Tells him he is ending it. This is the last battle. There will be no victor.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 setting up the stakes of the two witches in conflict. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Take me back! This is a violation of the treaty! I am needed on the battlefield.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So is she.\u8221\'94\line IT was right.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 You two will be all that is left. Cannot stop your eternal struggle. I would only wish that }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 He pops up into space. Gets the black.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 As the buried him, his last thought, which lasted for an infinity, was consider whether he, in his omniscience, omnipotence, could change his wants.}
